STATE
v.
Sherman Elwood SKIPPER. No. 122A92-5. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, Rex Gore, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of September 2005 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review Under G.S. 7A-31":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of October 2005."
